#### GAP-006: User Activity/Engagement Tracking

| Attribute | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **Gap** | No user-level activity tracking |
| **Business Impact** | Limited audience insights for creators |
| **Recommendation** | Add `user_activity` table |

**Proposed Table:**
```
user_activity
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── user_id (UUID, FK → users)
├── activity_type (VARCHAR) — 'page_view', 'post_view', 'profile_view', 'search', 'login'
├── entity_type (VARCHAR, nullable)
├── entity_id (UUID, nullable)
├── metadata (JSONB)
├── ip_address (INET)
├── user_agent (TEXT)
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

**Note:** HIGH VOLUME table — must be partitioned from day one.

