#### GAP-007: Content Bundles

| Attribute | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **Gap** | Cannot bundle content for purchase |
| **Business Impact** | Limited monetization options |
| **PRD Reference** | P1 feature - Content Bundles |
| **Recommendation** | Add bundle tables |

**Proposed Tables:**

**bundles:**
```
bundles
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── creator_id (UUID, FK → creator_profiles)
├── title (VARCHAR)
├── description (TEXT)
├── price (DECIMAL)
├── original_price (DECIMAL)
├── cover_image_url (TEXT)
├── status (VARCHAR) — 'draft', 'active', 'archived'
├── purchase_count (INTEGER)
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
├── updated_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

**bundle_items:**
```
bundle_items
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── bundle_id (UUID, FK → bundles)
├── post_id (UUID, FK → posts)
├── sort_order (INTEGER)
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

**bundle_purchases:**
```
bundle_purchases
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── bundle_id (UUID, FK → bundles)
├── user_id (UUID, FK → users)
├── transaction_id (UUID, FK → transactions)
├── price_paid (DECIMAL)
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
├── UNIQUE(bundle_id, user_id)
```

